cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.BIO, cs.CV 

The paper discusses the application of deep learning techniques for seizure prediction using EEG data. This falls under the domain of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of bidirectional LSTM networks is a popular technique in neural networks (cs.NE) and has been applied successfully in various domains including speech recognition and natural language processing. The paper also deals with biomedical data (cs.BIO) and computer vision (cs.CV) techniques for analyzing EEG signals. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.BIO, and cs.CV.
